Title: PSM Dhivehi FM
Description: Dhivehi FM is the music radio channel of PSM. Formed on 1 April 2006, the channel mainly offers entertainment programs targeting youth. Public service messages and awareness issues are often highlighted through entertainment programs.

Title: PSM Dheenuge Adu
Description: Dheenuge Adu is a 24 hour radio channel by the Public Service Media of the Maldives. It is aimed at delivering content that would be strengthening awareness on Islam as a religion and firm-up the Islamic Aqeeda. The broadcast of Dheenuge' Adu can be received at 90.0 MHz.

Title: PSM Dhivehiraajjeyge Adu
Description: Voice of Maldives. Dhivehiraajjeyge Adu is the premier radio channel of PSM. As a public service broadcaster, the channel's content is based on educating, informing and entertaining listeners. Established on 29th December 1962, Dhivehiraajjeyge Adu is transmitted on MW 1449 KHz

Title: VFM 99
Description: The channel covers news, sports, entertainment, and informative programs. Broadcasting in Maldivian language
